name: Free Food! (Maynemotions Studios)
description:
Description

Free Food is about collecting food and avoiding the angry people who are chasing you. there are two areas of play, The inner area is inspired y the old cell phone game "Snake" however you can run and run out even double and triple jump. Get as much food as possible. 

Controls

Space Bar = Jump                  Double Jump= Space Bar x2                       Navigation = Mouse
